@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - Send/Accept/Reject Show Proposal

autonumber

actor "CRM Collaborator" as CRM
actor "Customer Representative" as CR
participant ":System" as System

== CRM sends a proposal ==

activate CRM
CRM -> System: requests to send a show proposal
activate System

System -> System: generates proposal document
System -> System: attaches video link (if available)
System -> System: updates proposal status to STAND_BY
System -> System: saves who sent it and when (audit)
System --> CRM: informs of successful sending
deactivate CRM

== Customer Representative accepts/rejects ==

activate CR
CR -> System: views received proposals
System -> System: retrieves proposals for the customer representative
System --> CR: shows list of proposals

CR -> System: sends accept or reject decision
System -> System: updates proposal status to ACCEPTED or REJECTED
System -> System: stores feedback (if provided)
System -> System: logs who made the decision and when (audit)
System --> CR: confirmation of decision saved

deactivate CR
deactivate System

@enduml